description: CryptFillCoin (CFC) is a blockchain based platform that is developed to offer the most cost-effective way of sending, receiving and storing various cryptocurrencies. It gives individuals and companies the ability to generate invoices, send and receive payments and create multi-currency wallets. By providing such a comprehensive platform for the crypto trading industry, CryptFillCoin aims to bring cryptocurrencies to the commercial marketplace.
name: CryptFillCoin
